data.description: Beautiful house located on Raintree Lake just 30 minutes S of St. Louis. This home is perfect to enjoy lake living at its finest w/a backyard Gazebo & plenty of entertainment space. When you walk in the front door you will immediately feel right at home. The open floor plan makes it great for entertaining complete w/fireplace. Large mstr bdrm w/full bath & walk in closet are just some of the features you will love .Did I mention the 6 bdrms & 3 full baths? This home has plenty of room for family or friends who want to stay for the weekend. Downstairs has family room &recreational room as well as walkout french doors & sidewalk leading directly down to the lake. The home has been very well maintained & the owner has taken pride in the landscaping which evident as you walk around the property. In addition, this home has the possibility to turn the basement into In Law Quarters. Raintree Country Club offers golf, swimming pool, exercise room & soon to open banquet & restaurant facilities.
